title: Mackenzie Dern goes from jiu-jitsu star to UFC Champion | ABOUT LAST FIGHT
description:
From Etihad Arena in Abu Dhabi, About Last Fight brings all of the big winners straight to you as soon as they exit the Octagon. New UFC strawweight Champion Mackenzie Dern sits down with Dan Hellie, McKenzie Pavacich, and Michael Bisping to talk about achieving her dream of winning UFC gold, sharing the moment with her daughter, and looking ahead to a new age at strawweight. Dan, McKenzie, and The Count also sit with Alexander Volkov, Umar Nurmagomedov, and Azamat Murzakanov. Tune in to find out who won the night and what's next for these UFC stars.

From T-Mobile Arena in Las Vegas, Nevada, About Last Fight brings all of the big winners straight to you as soon as they exit the Octagon.  New UFC Light Heavyweight Champion Alex Pereira sits down with Dan Hellie, McKenzie Pavacich, and Chris Weidman to recap his knockout of Magomed Ankalaev, as well as to set his sights on another major milestone in his fighting career.

Dan, McKenzie, and Chris also sit with defending UFC Bantamweight Champion Merab Dvalishvili, Jiri Prochazka, Youssef Zalal, and Joe Pyfer.  Tune in to find out who won the night and what's next for these UFC stars.
